{"tid":1044270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關sir真係走得好前，就好似陳巧文一樣","createTime":"2019-03-02T18:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T05:09:17.000Z","uid":19527,"like":102,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d00fd27c14d2326f20c8b5b6ff946fa3222052ee","tid":1044270,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:45:39.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇完成報老闆篇訪問話支那係香港各行各業都部署哂間諜，特工。<br />\n再見到好多人係華為比人踢爆邀請傳媒個post轉移視線<br />\n就明白關sir成日話人係五毛係冇錯<br />\n連登作為其中一個最活躍forum，中共點會唔倒人落黎搶話語權？<br />\n係華為個post見到好多明踩暗保/明撐華為既留言<br />\n就知道連登其實已經比中共入侵得好緊要<br />\n關sir雖然成日屈錯人，但佢既動機係完全正確。"},{"pid":"404824ac6a15c49b149f4a78fba4298cab9adad6","tid":1044270,"uid":24730,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T21:02:23.000Z","msg":"支持，關sir 可能有殺錯，但應該都捉到好多真五毛"},{"pid":"dcc0104642c2cd0010c78152c73f82a83bfc1f75","tid":1044270,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T21:47:41.000Z","msg":"冇得同陳巧文比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9296950626575a953b597e02a825bd5c6bc6161c","tid":1044270,"uid":57255,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T22:33:25.000Z","msg":"根本d五毛就好似坑渠老鼠，平時收得埋，一有事(例如今次咁)就屹個老鼠頭出黎帶風向/附和/踩埋一份<br />\n<br />\n你一係就全部唔好捉，由得連登俾班坑渠老鼠搞搞震<br />\n你一捉就會變成關愛座咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236c60f7a65cb8fe0c33c5aecc83d2664ce8a625","tid":1044270,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T23:28:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得已經唔需要5毛 港人已被同化"},{"pid":"5d629380401acf206910dce5baa48dc2d52956c7","tid":1044270,"uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T23:34:57.000Z","msg":"三日後，除左連登班鍵盤戰士，出面仲有人記得單野先算啦"},{"pid"